title: Spacious remodeled 2 bedroom, 2 bath apartment for rent
posting_body: ['Spacious remodeled 2 bedroom, 2 bath apartment for rent, If you interested to schedule a viewing', 'show contact info', 'Beautiful, furnished home on the bike path in a lovely neighborhood!', 'You will find plenty of room to enjoy in this home including a large, eat-in kitchen, living room and a separate living space, 2 bedrooms, a large office and 2 full bathrooms.', 'The basement has additional space and laundry area.', 'The open plan provides for comfort and light, and all rooms share the sweeping, The Unit is being rented out Unfurnished.', 'All The Staging Furniture were removed.', 'We have a friendly atmosphere of diverse tenants.', 'Included within our property is off street parking, an indoor pool, laundry facilities in unit.', 'We are within walking distance from major grocery stores, fast food restaurants, sit down restaurants, gas stations.', 'Outside you will enjoy the large backyard and the convenience of being able to hop on the bike path accessed at the rear of the yard.', 'There is an EV charging unit available..', 'New windows.', 'Also, includes an AC unit.', 'All utilities included (gas for heat, hot water and stove, electricity, Wi-Fi, cable, internet).', 'Tenant responsible for snow and trash removal.', 'No use of garage or woodstove.', 'No pets preferred and no smoking of any kind.', 'If you interested to schedule a viewing', 'show contact info']
